T1  - IVF outcome in anovulatory infertility (WHO group 2) - Including polycystic ovary syndrome - Following previous unsuccessful ovulation induction
A1  - Mulders A.G.M.G.J.
A1  - Laven J.S.E.
A1  - Imani B.
